      • sendStaticId

        public static void sendStaticId(String uniqueIdentifer,
                                Callback<Boolean> cb)
        Sends the users unique identifer as an encrypted string that will be registered with the current device

        This method can only be called after the Engagement service has been initialized using the Engagement.Builder.

        Parameters:
        uniqueIdentifer - The unique identifier sent to be registered with the device.
        cb - The user supplied callback for either success or failure of the call
